rows.label: qst100704_msg0001
rows.name:
Phwoar! Nunui acknowledge receipt
of one million of friend's finest G!

rows.label: qst100704_msg0002
rows.name:
Now I tear up I.O.U. paper...
And hand over treasures!

rows.label: qst100704_msg0003
rows.name:
Rex...
I'm sorry for the bother.

rows.label: qst100704_msg0005
rows.name:
You know I've got your back! I don't
even mind if you used the cash on
presents for your girlfriend!

rows.label: qst100704_msg0006
rows.name:
You understand, then?!
Yes, she was something of a
material girl... It was a difficult time.

rows.label: qst100704_msg0007
rows.name:
After the break-up, I never managed to
meet anyone new, so I've been single
for over a century now...

rows.label: qst100704_msg0008
rows.name: ...I was just trying to be funny...

rows.label: qst100704_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh.
S-sorry, maybe that was
too much information...

rows.label: qst100704_msg0010
rows.name:
Nunui offer commiserations,
but am frankly not overly interested.

rows.label: qst100704_msg0011
rows.name:
More importantly for Nunui,
can now use capital of one million G
to revive Pyrithium Trade Guild!

rows.label: qst100704_msg0012
rows.name:
Step one, as learned from wisdom of
Bahn, is employ adorable attendants!
Will get on it right away!
